<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Feliz Dia dos Namorados</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sacramento&family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap');

  html, body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #ff1c3f, #8b0000);
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    color: #fff;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  body {
    position: relative;
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 50px 40px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-radius: 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.6);
    max-width: 520px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    z-index: 10;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Sacramento', cursive;
    font-size: 5rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: #ff9aae;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(255, 20, 70, 0.8);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #ffccd5;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(255, 105, 135, 0.6);
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-top: 28px;
    color: #ffd1dc;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(60, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .hearts {
    margin: 40px auto 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 22px;
    font-size: 3.8rem;
    color: #ff1a48;
    animation: pulse 1.8s infinite ease-in-out alternate;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px #ff1a48);
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0% {
      transform: scale(1);
      color: #ff4a68;
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px #ff4a68;
    }
    100% {
      transform: scale(1.35);
      color: #ff1a48;
      text-shadow: 0 0 24px #ff1a48;
    }
  }

  .floating-hearts {
    position: fixed;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    -webkit-user-select: none;
    color: #ff1a48;
    font-size: 28px;
    animation-timing-function: linear;
    animation-iteration-count: infinite;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px #ff1a48);
    z-index: 5;
  }

  /* background subtle heart shapes */
  .heart-background {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    width: 150vw;
    height: 150vh;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 2;
    opacity: 0.12;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle, #ff1a48 15%, transparent 16%),
      radial-gradient(circle, #ff4a68 15%, transparent 16%);
    background-position: 10% 30%, 80% 70%;
    background-repeat: repeat;
    background-size: 80px 80px;
    animation: heartFloatBG 15s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes heartFloatBG {
    0% {
      background-position: 10% 30%, 80% 70%;
    }
    100% {
      background-position: 10% 10%, 80% 110%;
    }
  }

</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="heart-background" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="container" role="main" aria-label="Mensagem de Dia dos Namorados">
    <h1>Para Voc√™, Meu Amor ‚ù§Ô∏è</h1>
    <h2>Feliz Dia dos Namorados!</h2>
    <p>
      Cada dia ao seu lado meu cora√ß√£o bate mais forte. Que nosso amor aumente cada vez mais, cheio de carinho, risadas e infinitos abra√ßos. Voc√™ √© tudo pra mim, minha inspira√ß√£o, e meu sonho que se tornou realidade, Eu te amo!
    </p>
    <div class="hearts" aria-hidden="true">
      <span>‚ù§Ô∏è</span>
      <span>üíñ</span>
      <span>üíï</span>
      <span>üíó</span>
      <span>üíò</span>
      <span>‚ù£Ô∏è</span>
      <span>üíì</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    const heartEmojis = ['‚ù§Ô∏è', 'üíñ', 'üíï', 'üíó', 'üíò', '‚ù£Ô∏è', 'üíì'];

    function createFloatingHeart() {
      const heart = document.createElement('div');
      heart.classList.add('floating-hearts');
      heart.textContent = heartEmojis[Math.floor(Math.random() * heartEmojis.length)];
      heart.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';

      // Larger size range for vibrant presence
      const size = 18 + Math.random() * 40;
      heart.style.fontSize = size + 'px';

      heart.style.animationDuration = (4 + Math.random() * 4) + 's';
      // start at bottom viewport
      heart.style.top = '100vh';

      document.body.appendChild(heart);

      heart.animate([
        { transform: `translateY(0)`, opacity: 1 },
        { transform: `translateY(-120vh)`, opacity: 0 }
      ], {
        duration: 7000 + Math.random() * 4000,
        easing: 'linear'
      });

      setTimeout(() => {
        heart.remove();
      }, 11000);
    }
    // Increase hearts frequency to make it more full of hearts
    setInterval(createFloatingHeart, 200);
  </script>
</body>
</html>

